               <history>
                  <origin notBefore="1700" notAfter="1725" cert="high">
                     <p>Skrifað af séra <name
                           key="FraIbs001" type="person">Frans Íbssyni</name> (sbr. <ref type="ms"
                              target="#AM02-0477-da">AM 477 fol.</ref>, bl. 31r og  <ref type="ms" target="AM02-0456-da">AM 456 fol.</ref>, bl. 19r) og tímasett til upphafs
                           <origDate notBefore="1700" notAfter="1725" cert="high">18.
                           aldar</origDate> (<bibl><ref target="KKKat">Katalog</ref> (I)</bibl> 1889:<ref
                           target="https://baekur.is/bok/c9ff2011-3cda-4197-90ef-7e14fc19f264/1/628"
                           >612</ref>). Eftirrit eftir handriti sem <name key="JonErl001"
                           type="person">Jón Erlendsson</name> í Villingaholti skrifaði og <name
                           key="GudÞor001" type="person">Guðrún Þorgilsdóttir</name> á Ingjaldshóli
                        átti.</p>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>
                     <p>Árið <date when="1730">1730</date> var handritið hluti af No 408 in 4to (sbr. AM 456 fol., bl. 19r; AM 477 fol., bl. 31r).</p>
